---
const points = [
  {
    title: 'California legal-office workflow',
    body: 'Our process is shaped by practical paralegal experience in a California law-firm environment: organized intake, clean document packets, evidence checklists, and review-ready files.'
  },
  {
    title: 'Official-source checks',
    body: 'USCIS and California court form references are checked against official sources before document preparation begins, so clients are not relying on stale file names or copied PDFs.'
  },
  {
    title: 'Multilingual intake',
    body: 'Clients can explain their situation in English, Russian, Ukrainian, or Spanish. The workflow keeps form codes and legal boundaries clear while making the questions easier to answer.'
  },
  {
    title: 'Client-directed preparation',
    body: 'We prepare documents at the client’s direction. Imverica is not a law firm, does not give legal advice, and does not choose legal strategy for the client.'
  }
];
---
<section class="why-section" id="why-imverica">
  <div class="why-inner">
    <div class="why-copy">
      <div class="why-kicker">Why Imverica</div>
      <h2>Built for real document-preparation work, not generic forms.</h2>
      <p>
        Imverica combines California document-preparation discipline, multilingual intake, and official-source form checks so clients can move from “what do I need?” to an organized document packet.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-grid">
      {points.map((point) => (
        <article class="why-card">
          <h3>{point.title}</h3>
          <p>{point.body}</p>
        </article>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .why-section {
    background: #fffaf2;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(40, 30, 20, 0.08);
    padding: var(--space-section) 1.5rem;
  }

  .why-inner {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(280px, 0.8fr) minmax(360px, 1.2fr);
    gap: 32px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .why-kicker {
    color: var(--terracotta-deep);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 1.6px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .why-copy h2 {
    font-size: var(--fs-h2);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .why-copy p,
  .why-card p {
    color: #3a4a5e;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .why-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .why-card {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid rgba(40, 30, 20, 0.1);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 22px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 22px rgba(40, 30, 20, 0.05);
  }

  .why-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-system);
    font-size: 17px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 8px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 820px) {
    .why-inner,
    .why-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .why-section {
      padding: var(--space-section) 1.25rem;
    }
  }
</style>
